      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior paint still holds a great shine, though there are some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with regular driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and the upholstery is in great shape, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics and mechanical systems are functioning as they should, making this a reliable and attractive option for its next owner.",
