      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of character? This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for a new owner who appreciates a solid, functional car that's been driven and enjoyed. It\u2019s a great choice for someone seeking reliable transportation and real value!",
