      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a pristine E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM ceiling. This unit is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The undercarriage is immaculate, with verified subframe integrity and refreshed bushings throughout. Every mechanical component, from the high-pressure VANOS lines to the cooling system's expansion tank, has been maintained to factory tolerances. This is an investment-grade driver\u2019s car with zero deferred maintenance.",
